          "contentType": "purpose",
          "lang": "fr",
          "value": "Explorer la contribution de certaines pollutions et nuisances environnementales aux inégalités sociales de santé, notamment la santé périnatale"
        },
        {
          "contentType": "purpose",
          "lang": "en",
          "value": "Explore the contribution of certain environmental pollution and disturbances to social inequalities in health, including perinatal health"
